{"type": "article", "id": 10064, "title": "Robert van Embricqs 飞桌", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-27T07:37:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235445iCFrUJ1hG7kdcX5j.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tRobert van Embricqs 有一个 “Rising Furniture” 系列，都可以在复杂优美的造型和平整的桌子之间进行自由的转换，这次他又推出了一个“桌上桌”，通过轻质的铰链设计，可以让桌子像一个花苞一样升起。这是 <a href=\"http://www.robertvanembricqs.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Robert van Embricqs 的个人主页</a>，点击这里可以查看更多 “Rising Furniture” 系列的作品，感受 Robert van Embricqs 对这种复杂造型的醉心。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235443uAJzEQBlaMKoZc5H.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.69583333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235443SZ2lWgHFERGbtuiL.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052354448nklQFXYvDNpAw3K.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.84270833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}